text: What time of day are you most proficient at programming?
For some reason I find that I am at my best, in terms of programming, late at night.
I'm not sure if it's because I lose my inhibition that keeps me from pushing forward or if there is something else to it but either way I get the most done after the sun goes down.
What time of day do you find yourself the most proficient in terms of programming?
